You can use only an if-then-else type.
Examples:

sineValue = Math.sin(2 * Math.PI * i * 440 / 44100.0);
if (sineValue >= 0) {
    y = 1;
} else {
    y = -1;
}

Which converts a sinusoidal wave into a quadratic wave.

You can use only an if-then-else type.
Examples:

if (x % 100 < 50) {
    y = 1;
} else {
    y = -1;
}
Note: this code gives the same result for a quadratic wave of 440Hz.
